---
title: Herby Pork Sausage & Apple Slaw Subs with Cheesy Wedges, Dill-Parsley Mayo & Onion Chutney
description: Bangers in a bun, it’s hot dogs done up to the nines tonight! Fill up your buns with herby pork sausages, a fragrant creamy layer of herby mayo and a sweet apple slaw. Serve with wedges to finish off this upgraded classic.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651df6535dddf9d92d88d646-df90ea64-f1af2163.jpeg
